# Generated pipeline outputs.
# data/eval/ (frozen eval items) IS versioned. The final 3 corpora + their provenance
# (.meta.json) + validation_report.json ARE committed for transparency. Generation
# byproducts and superseded runs are not.
data/corpora/*.rejects.jsonl
data/corpora/_archive*/
data/corpora/pilot/
data/corpora/smoke/
runs/*
!runs/.gitkeep

# Local social-post drafts — not committed
SOCIAL_POSTS.md
